<main>
    <section class="showcase" id="showcase">
        <form id="image-form">
          <h1 class="AI">IMAGE DESCRIPTION</h1>
          <div class="form-control">
            <input type="text" id="prompt" placeholder="Enter Text" />
          </div>

          <!-- Input User API -->


            <!-- Input User API -->

            <div class="get-api-text">
              <p>
                You can get your API key from:
                <a target="_blank" href="https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys">Open AI API key</a>
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-control">
              <input id="api-key" type="text" id="api-key" placeholder="Enter your API key" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-control">
              <select name="size" id="size">
                <option value="small">Small</option>
                <option value="medium" selected>Medium</option>
                <option value="large">Large</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="formBtns">
              <button type="submit" class="btn" aria-label="generate">
                <span>Generate</span>
                <div class="flow"></div>
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="btn" id="surpriseMeBtn" aria-label="surprise me">
                <span>Surprise Me!</span>
                <div class="flow"></div>
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </section>
        <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
          <h3 style="text-align:center; padding-top: 1rem ; font-size: xx-large;color:white;">Frequently Asked Questions
          </h3>
          <h3 style="text-align:center; padding-bottom: 2rem ;font-weight: 300; color:white;">Learn More About
            Imagine-AI and Get Started Today!</h3>
          <div class="container2">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">What is Imagine-AI</div>
              <div class="answer">
                <p>
                  Imagine-ai is startup that uses AI, including DALL·E2, to convert text into stunning images. We
                  empower users to effortlessly transform their ideas into visually captivating content, revolutionizing
                  communication and storytelling. With Imagine-AI, bridge the gap between text and visuals with our
                  cutting-edge AI technology.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container2">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">What does DALL-E 2 Open AI refer to</div>
              <div class="answer">
                <p>
                  DALL·E 2 is OpenAI's advanced AI model that generates high-quality images from textual descriptions,
                  surpassing the capabilities of its predecessor, DALL·E. It utilizes deep learning techniques to push
                  the boundaries of AI-generated imagery.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container2">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">How to obtain your API Key to genertae Image</div>
              <div class="answer">
                <p>
                  To get your DALL-E 2 API key, follow these steps :<br>
                  (1) Go to the OpenAI website and sign up for an account. <br>
                  (2) Once you have signed up, navigate to your account settings by clicking on your account name and
                  selecting "API Keys" from the drop-down menu.<br>
                  (3) On the "API Keys" page, you will find your API key. Copy and save it for future use.<br>
                  (4) It is recommended to save your API key as an environment variable or in a secure location </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container2">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">How to generate Images using Imagine-AI</div>
              <div class="answer">
                <p>
                  To Generate Images using Imagine-AI, follow these steps :<br>
                  (1) Go To Imagine-AI Page.<br>
                  (2) Enter the Text, corresponding to the Image.<br>
                  (3) Enter your API Key.<br>
                  (4) Select the size of the Image you want, and click on Generate.
                  (4) Click on Generate.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container2">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">What is the Suprise Me Button for</div>
              <div class="answer">
                <p>
                  Suprise Me! , an option which generates text for you and after you've entered your API Key and size,
                  amazing visuals are seen, Try it to unlock the suprise there for you.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <script>
          const container2 = document.getElementsByClassName('accordion');
          for (i = 0; i < container2.length; i++) {
            container2[i].addEventListener('click', function () {
              this.classList.toggle('active')
            })
          }
        </script>
        <section>
          <div class="popup-container" id="popup">
            <img src="./faviconicon/erroricon.webp" alt="error">
            <h4 id="text"></h4>
            <button class="popup-btn" onclick="closePopUp()" aria-label="click ok"><span>OK</span></span>
              <div class="flow"></div>
            </button>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="image">
          <div class="image-container">
            <h2 class="msg"></h2>
            <img src="" alt="" id="image" />
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
      <div class="spinner"></div>

